data.description:
Available again! Enjoy 2nd level elevation in a fantastic location & with stress free living! 2nd floor is the perfect floor to be on...easy to exit and still elevated! 5 mins to Fort Meade NSA BWI 295 95. 3 mins to Arundel Mills Mall Cinemark Theaters Casino Live Walmart Costco Bank of America Staples 30+ restaurants: Chipotle Chick-Fil-A Starbucks Baja Fresh Cheesecake Factory TGI Fridays Red Lobster & much more. See map in pics. 2 Secure entrances & elevator open living space w/1400+ sq ft with 2 bedrooms & 2 full baths w/master double vanity walk-in master closet sun room outdoor patio and windows faces lots of natural light all day with sun setting on patio side!
Recently updated appliances: microwave, dish washer, gas stove, and new smart washer & dryer.

Available for rent and sale
data.whatILove: Perfect location and angle of unit provides abundance of natural light and cool breeze all day with windows open during the summer. Convenient to everything! Less than 5 minutes to Arundel Mills Mall, entertainment, grocery, and restaurants. BWI Airport 14 minutes away.
